document.discussion_title: EMS: Motorcyclist injured in wreck in Southeast Austin
document.topic_text: EMS: Motorcyclist injured in wreck in Southeast Austin American-Statesman Monday 25th April, 2016 A collision between a motorcycle and another vehicle resulted in a man, thought to be in his 40s, being taken to the hospital Sunday.Austin-Travis County EMS responded to the collision at Thaxton Road and Panadero Drive in Southeast Austin shortly after 1 p.m.Medics have taken the driver of the motorcycle to St. David's South Austin Hospital with potentially serious injuries. No other injuries were reported....
